&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>80/tcp open http syn-ack
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>Enumerated open TCP ports:&lt;/p>
